    <string name="about">About</string>
    <string name="app_description">EmerBand is a comprehensive emergency solution designed to keep you safe. It works with a BLE smart watch to monitor your safety and trigger emergency protocols when needed. The app provides multiple safety features including fake calls, connecting cyber cell, and sending emergency alerts with GPS coordinates.</string>
    <string name="key_features">Key Features:</string>
    <string name="features_list">• Emergency alerts with GPS coordinates\n• Fake call simulation for distress signals\n• Cyber cell alert for digital threats\n• SMS/Location alerts system for emergencies\n• Offline mode for storing emergency events</string>
    <string name="developed_by">Developed by Abhay</string>
    
