    <string name="faqs">Frequently Asked Questions</string>
    <string name="faq_1_title">How does the emergency alert system work?</string>
    <string name="faq_1_content">When you trigger an emergency alert, the app automatically sends your current location to your emergency contacts via SMS and initiates an emergency call. The app also activates a loud siren to attract attention.</string>
    <string name="faq_2_title">What should I do if the app isn\'t detecting my smartwatch?</string>
    <string name="faq_2_content">First, ensure Bluetooth is enabled on your phone. If the issue persists, try disconnecting and reconnecting your smartwatch. For further assistance, contact our support team.</string>
